Class DataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.util.geometry.shapes.VPoint
      • org.vadere.util.geometry.DataPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<VPoint>

    public class DataPoint
extends VPoint
implements java.lang.Comparable<VPoint>
    Point class representing one VPoint in 2D space with an additional double-valued data store. An order can be applied with the isGreaterThan method.
